

[http://www.haskell.org/arrows/]

An abstraction of computations, more general than monads.

[GHC]() provides [support for the notation](http://www.haskell.org/ghc/docs/7.2.1/html/users_guide/arrow-notation.html) described in the link above, it can be turned on using ''-XArrows'' command-line flag.

